'''酸养互营菌'''，[[革兰氏阴性|革兰氏阴性]][[杆菌|杆菌]]。它不能[[能动性|移动]]，不会产[[孢子|孢]]，只能在严格厌氧条件下生长，因而是[[专性厌氧菌|专性厌氧菌]]。在与耗氢微生物[[互养|互养]]时能降解脂肪酸和[[苯甲酸|苯甲酸]]<ref name=benzo>{{cite journal | last1 = Elshahed | first1 = M. S. | last2 = McInerney | first2 = M. J. | title = Benzoate Fermentation by the Anaerobic Bacterium Syntrophus aciditrophicus in the Absence of Hydrogen-Using Microorganisms | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_applied-and-environmental-microbiology_2001-12_67_12/page/5520 | journal = Applied and Environmental Microbiology | volume = 67 | issue = 12 | year = 2001 | pages = 5520–5525 | issn = 0099-2240 | doi = 10.1128/AEM.67.12.5520-5525.2001}}</ref>。其基因组于2007年发表<ref name="McInerneyRohlin2007">{{cite journal | last1 = McInerney | first1 = M. J. | last2 = Rohlin | first2 = L. | last3 = Mouttaki | first3 = H. | last4 = Kim | first4 = U. | last5 = Krupp | first5 = R. S. | last6 = Rios-Hernandez | first6 = L. | last7 = Sieber | first7 = J. | last8 = Struchtemeyer | first8 = C. G. | last9 = Bhattacharyya | first9 = A. | last10 = Campbell | first10 = J. W. | last11 = Gunsalus | first11 = R. P. | title = The genome of Syntrophus aciditrophicus: Life at the thermodynamic limit of microbial growth | journal = Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences | volume = 104 | issue = 18 | year = 2007 | pages = 7600–7605 | issn = 0027-8424 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.0610456104}}</ref>。

